name: Cellshock (RhinoWarlord)
description:
Playable and is a finished prototype (with some minor bugs).

Not the final design choices, far from the would-be product that I had in mind.

Focus on customizing your nanobot, that's the main part :D

CHEAT CODE: Press F1 to get a lot of samples, this allows you to fill up the sample bar and unlock customization.
